  "description": "Update Base Path Configuration for Local Development\n\nFix navigation links that are currently broken in the local development environment due to a base path mismatch between the server configuration and client-side routing.\n\nRequirements:\n- Update all internal links to use the correct base path `/wesole_nutki/` when running locally\n- Identify and update hardcoded absolute paths (starting with `/`) to include the base path\n- Implement a configurable base path solution that works for both local (`/wesole_nutki/`) and production (`/`) environments\n- Update routing configuration to respect the base path\n- Update asset references (CSS, JS, images) to use the correct base path\n- Test all navigation links, redirects, and deep linking to ensure they work correctly\n- Consider using environment variables or build configuration to manage different base paths per environment",
